Module org.autogui
Package org.autogui.base.log

Class GuiLogEntryProgress

java.lang.Object
org.autogui.base.log.GuiLogEntryProgress
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, AutoCloseable, GuiLogEntry
Direct Known Subclasses:
GuiSwingLogEntryProgress
public class GuiLogEntryProgress extends Object implements GuiLogEntry, Closeable
a log-entry for progress: 
     [time] minimum|=========value - - - - |maximum : valueP %, message
     or
     [time] |- - - indeterminate - - - | message
     =>
     [time] message
     [endTime] 100%
